# Backend Rules

Follow [`docs/backend.md`](../../docs/backend.md) and [`docs/project-conventions.md`](../../docs/project-conventions.md).

- Thin controllers; business logic in `application/services/`.
- All MongoDB access through repository ports — no Mongoose in controllers or routes.
- Use `ITagRepository` for mood categories (`tags` collection), not a separate categories collection.
- Public DTOs must exclude `authorId`, `userId`, and `email`.
